{"type": "article", "id": 6281, "title": "夜幕下的华尔街", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t白天是世界金融中心的华尔街，在夜晚就是最寂寞的地方。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在常驻华盛顿的摄影师 <a href=\"http://jseawell.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Jay Turner Frey Seawell</a> 的镜头里，夜幕之下的黑白华尔街也许是更真实的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213722KBn41FGthN0lzwZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213723JQtIun5x6FfsWYTD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213723XNv7tP0lofKFHQy4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213723iHXo1AZV8R0YeDWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"1.504\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213724dkNL8OvfBzt0TJ39.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213724EthmwxcM1XR3T7WY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213725z9nXjF0cPa5Wx3Il.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"1.506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042137257HoLOCh0JuUPyzw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"0.659\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604213726synvUefIAlgFx6Mb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\" data-ratio=\"1.502\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20